quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  12,5,"[Baaba makko] maaki: "Eehey ma …ìinngel am, wota a fillano musi…ó…ìe maa …ìen koy…óol maa ngol sakko …ìe fewjane feere; pellet seytaane ko ga√±o aade …ìanngu…óo(.pee√±…óo.)"
  12,6,"Ko wano nii Joomi maa su…ìoray maa, O anndinma firo koy…ói, o timmina dokke makko on e maa…óa e …ìeynguure Yaaquuba nden, wano o timminirnoo mo e baabiraa…ìe maa …ìen …ói…óo: Ibraahiima e ishaaqa. Pellet Joomi maa ko ganndu…óo √ëee√±…óo."
  12,7,"Goo≈ã…óii wonii e Yuusufa e musi…ó…ìe makko …ìeen, taskuyeeji wonan¬¥de la…ìndotoo…ìe …ìen."
  12,8,"tuma nde …ìe mbi'noo: "Pellet ko Yuusufa e neene-gooto(musi…ó…óo )mun on …ìuraa yi…óeede ka ben-men dii enen, enen le ko en jamaa …óuu…óu…ìe. Pellet baabamen wonii e majjere …ìanngunde"."
  12,9,"Mbaree Yuusufa maa fero…óon mo e leydi; yeeso baaba mon ngon heeranoo on, ngonton …ìaawo …óum yim…ìe mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe"."
  12,10,"Gooto e ma…ì…ìe wi'i: "Wota on mbarYuusufa, mbeddee mo ka ni…ìe woyndu yoga e setee…ìe hoccay mo, si on laatike golloo…ìe"."
  12,11,"∆Åe mbi'i: "eeheyma baaba amen, ko he…ìu-maa a hoolotaako amen e fii Yuusufa? Minen le ko men laa…ìam…ìe mo reedu"."
  12,12,"Accitid-mo e amen o √±aama, o fija,minen ko men reenoo…ìe mo."
  12,13,"O maaki: "miin no suninat kam nde njahdoton e makko; mi…óo huli nde boyeeru ndu √±aamata-mo tawa Ko on mbelsindi-…óoon e makko"."
  12,14,"∆Åe mbi'i: "Pellet si saafaandu √±aamii mo e hoore ko men jamaa …óuu…óu…ìe, haray ko men hayru…ìe"(pertu…ìe.)"